	<title2><![CDATA[Aligning with the Customer’s Needs]]></title2>
	<instructions><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:11pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:bold; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px">You are at your meeting with Dr. Cardonza at Maycomb Community Hospital. With you is Dr. Gomez, who has been your main contact in the cardiology department.  After establishing rapport, you reviewed the agenda for the meeting.  Now it is time to kick off your discussion with a question. Which question will you ask Dr. Cardonza first?</welcomeText>]]></instructions>
	<choices>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[1]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>A</b>. During my previous talks with Dr. Gomez, we’ve discussed therapy and treatment options for hyponatremia.  Can you tell me more about the opportunities for treating hyponatremia that you see?</welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="10">
				<KPI marks="10"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="-10"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="10"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R2_D010_A010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		<choice>
