			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>B</b>. With the ongoing healthcare reform and increasing regulations, what issues do you see potentially affecting your department?</welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="-10">
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="-10"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
