			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>C</b>. It sounds like maintaining your department’s reputation is one of your top priorities.  What are your next steps to address that priority?  </welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
