			<isCorrect><![CDATA[YES]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>D</b>. From previous conversations with Dr. Gomez, I’ve learned that you want to continue building your department’s reputation and stay at the forefront of medical advances.  As part of achieving those goals, what are the treatment goals you desire for your patients with hyponatremia? </welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
